{"tid":1564290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 召喚 8月23日出現係英皇道西灣河既手足","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:24:55.000Z","uid":125782,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9ce6dd84c80a20eb40791cf0668717a89dcd4e","tid":1564290,"uid":125782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:51:21.000Z","msg":"事發片段(由fb :melly chxn轉貼) :   <br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/359567418\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F359567418&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=ef23009c\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/359567418</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/359567819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F359567819&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=19206e9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/359567819</a><br />\n片主為背紅色袋中年女子 (藍絲)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SY3i8EV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSY3i8EV.png&h=c9105d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事件發生係上個月23日英皇道西灣河 大約晚上9~10點, 片主同途人對罵<br />\n<br />\n想搵片中當時在場既手足, 有關任何在場拍攝既影片/照片, 如果片中係你認識既人,請麻煩傳遞訊息。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事關小弟現正向該名片主作出法律途徑追究,需要更多證據,資料, 希望大家可以幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n該名中年女子亦多次係FACEBOOK上同不同分身A/C誣捏抹黑本人,本人保留一切追究權利 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mokmok14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmokmok14&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=c01f59e3\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/mokmok14</a>"},{"pid":"33e3558ee44c4172ea727c782c2c3a3a02f78262","tid":1564290,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\